{"id":285325,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-长沙公民申请集会示威遭拒，提起行政复/","date":"2013-03-21T12:30:49Z","modified":"2013-03-21T12:30:49Z","title":"维权网 | 长沙公民申请集会示威遭拒，提起行政复议（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div align=\"left\"><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）本网此前报道，</span>3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>，长沙市包括吴莎、李香、段静玲等数十位曾被非法关押、非法拘禁、被限制人身自由的公民，来到长沙市公安局递交了关于游行集会的申请书，要求在贺龙体育广场举行</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>人规模的静坐示威，以表达促进长沙依法行政、维护公民合法权利的诉求。</span></p>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>下午，长沙市公安局治安管理治安大队二大队副队长熊浩通知吴莎等人来拿关于游行集会申请的回复，回复是不予许可，说在贺龙体育广场静坐示威将直接危害公共安全，破坏社会秩序。众人质疑说，贺龙体育广场那么大，去</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>万人也不会影响秩序。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>下午，集会静坐的申请被不予许可后，吴莎等人来到长沙市政府法制科递交了行政复议，接待工作人员接受并要求填写了行政复议文书送达地址确认表。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>不过一位了解情况的访民说，这种行政复议长沙市政府部门从来就没输过。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>参见：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2013/03/blog-post_2902.html</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-AMIxuoMxsrs/UUrF7Ok59PI/AAAAAAAAfEE/ODNOjXLiPZc/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-AMIxuoMxsrs/UUrF7Ok59PI/AAAAAAAAfEE/ODNOjXLiPZc/s400/1.jpg\" width=\"323\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-AMXr0pBud1c/UUrF8tot_SI/AAAAAAAAfEM/HacneVyYwNM/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\